<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1918-09-14T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1918-09-14T00:00:00-05:00" n="93" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d93">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 893.001H85/1</note>
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss>
                                    to the Chinese Minister</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Koo</hi></persName>)</head>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right">
                                    <placeName>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1918-09-14">
                                        <hi rend="italic">September 14, 1918</hi></date>.</dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I have the honor to acknowledge the
                                receipt of your note No. 74 of the 5th instant, in which, by
                                instruction of your Government, <pb facs="0222" n="110" xml:id="pg_110"/> you advised me that His Excellency Hsü
                                Shih-ch’ang has been elected President of the Republic of China for
                                the next term in accordance with the laws of that Republic.</p>
                            <p>Thanking you for the information contained in your note, of which due
                                note has been taken, I beg [etc.]</p>
                            <closer>
                                <signed>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Robert Lansing</hi>
                                </signed>
                            </closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>